Make sure the radio is connected to a the computer AND to a power source
Open the FRC Radio Configuration Utility
    - if the computer does not have this application, download it from here (don't download the Israel one):
    https://docs.wpilib.org/en/stable/docs/zero-to-robot/step-3/radio-programming.html
Follow the instructions on the app, fill in the information required
    - Team Number: 5498
    - Robot Name
    - we do not have a WPA Key
    - Radio: Open Mesh
    - Mode: 2.4GHz Access Point
    
Refer to the website above if there are further issues
